TortoiseHg Nemo Extension (based on tortoisehg-nautilus 2.10-1)

This extension is meant to be used with the Nemo File Manager,

Requirements:
    * nemo
    * nemo-python (not required from Mint 18 / Cinnamon 3.x on)
    * tortoisehg

To install:
    To install for all users, copy nemo-thg.py to:
        /usr/share/nemo-python/extensions
    
    To install for a single user, copy nemo-thg.py to:
        ~/.local/share/nemo-python-extensions
    
    In both cases, you may need to create the python/python-extensions folder.
    
    Restart nemo with the following commands:
        $ nemo -q

